description: Kotak Mahindra Mutual Fund - Kotak NV 20 ETF is an exchange traded fund launched by Kotak Mahindra Bank Limited. It is managed by Kotak Mahindra Asset Management Company Limited. The fund invests in the public equity markets of India. It seeks to invest in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in the value stocks of large-cap companies. It seeks to replicate the performance of the NV 20 Index, by investing in the stocks of companies as per their weightings in the index. Kotak Mahindra Mutual Fund - Kotak NV 20 ETF was formed on November 12, 2015 and is domiciled in India.
name: Kotak Nifty 50 Value 20 ETF
